{"tid":1243864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲嘢想提一提出嚟抗爭，但企後排嘅人","createTime":"2019-06-19T15:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T18:07:33.000Z","uid":226192,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30823210bf2e102bb8072de39af3318ee81c8dfb","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"以612龍和道做例子，前線頂緊班狗仔，後排叫極都唔嚟幫手。咁理解嘅，大家都驚，之不過請大家聽到前線嗌撤嘅時候行快兩步，前面仲有位行就千祈唔好停。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行快兩步</span><br />\n<br />\n上之明明AIA摩天輪到大把位、碼頭大把位，但大家就係死硬都唔行快啲，搞到前線義士硬食。<br />\n<br />\n明白兄弟爬山，各自出力。但請畀啲保障前線手足，佢哋真係攞個身出嚟幫大家頂住。<br />\n<br />\n希望下次再有咩事嘅時候，大家會拎到讓救護車行嘅嗰種速度，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有秩序、有節奏、有速度</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n有事起上嚟，大家撤得越快，啲義士都會相對安全啲，多謝大家。"},{"pid":"7451ee28da10c59caceb465c40b6f62b50ddbd33","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"各自出力嘅同時，嘗試理解下前線手足點解咁做，然後再慢慢討論戰術。大家加油。"},{"pid":"d2bf2fceb655340fef912988654ed0d78809c7eb","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d6397711610c475ff479ada89bcbb14496383e1","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"185d2759f12d56623ebb8ea974171b7bb7261b81","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee61c900cde3d27ad2d00975692b084be4358b48","tid":1243864,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b0dfe4332580c51f7d48517ae377c6226950d0b","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb935c09e5c7a01540480b8029d792b589630bd8","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99814a4bc98bd177a2d58337237bd98c2bd2a328","tid":1243864,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:53:28.000Z","msg":"人民就是力量"},{"pid":"eb6a3600536552415e64d95001deb96ed6bba28d","tid":1243864,"uid":235671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"336b3947ec764a19ee95512faba21b582fdb8aa3","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"大家加油，千祈唔好令前線心寒，大家喺同一條船"},{"pid":"7db321abce1ee42afe9024ed5d0157f7d0e64dec","tid":1243864,"uid":117886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"前線勇士加油!"},{"pid":"0385045a0d2a5a68cf54ec9e3eb9963b17426e95","tid":1243864,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3e43c7c55cae7d1b95a669957e0db0aa385172e3","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26e131c4950fd0aaa2c7d53c10f1d0f2b25111b3","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58fcc5eb32b0ce7927a78218e76e2374e6cd0da9","tid":1243864,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea6630f57b56a0f5081c2cddd7fdbb319d3ee48a","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d010326b049e5cbc735dbb40882041cf81c0100a","tid":1243864,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd6dc363003c5b96db77cbd9442a070744e4248f","tid":1243864,"uid":209516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3d6d9efaa633b2952885a8887c2d9ad3167ebf6","tid":1243864,"u